seller.description:
Hi, we are Artmazigh team from Indonesia.
Our specialization is illustration that is original and you never met before.
We can bring your concepts into life :D

We have been working with thousand of people from different backgrounds, such as musicians, politicians, soldiers, fire fighters, gamers, athletes and many more.

We guarantee you the best design and best experience you can get from Fiverr, especially from us, Artmazigh.

Should you have any questions, please don't hesitate to contact us.
We will always be ready for serving you.

Have a nice day.

reviews.comment: This experience has been on of the best service ever gotten from this site, any one that comes across this seller has to get his services. Very respectful person with a creative mind, if i have to get another logo this were i would come back.

ARTMAZIGH Team does such a fantastic job. The logo and animation video turned out great. I've hired them three other times and they never disappoint. Thank you for your talent and dedication to the craft. This is probably one of the best teams I've had the pleasure of working with. Can't wait to see what we do next!

Seller is patient and responds promptly. We had numerous requests and revisions but the seller managed to meet all of them. My advise is to compile any changes you would like together in a list as he might miss some if they are send in different messages. Would engage the artist again for future projects

This is a design that has been in my head for almost 20 years. Since I was a young man I had dreamed of this image. The image of the Mycenaean warrior ready to fight is the image I have chosen to represent my company and the artist every step of the way showed me that they not only care about what the image is but why this image. Will return 4 more
Even with my terrible explanation of what I wanted,  this team was able to crank our a fantastic piece in just a few days. I look forward to our continuing partnership.
